detailedDescription.articleBody: Sarah Jane Hazlegrove is an English actress, best known for portraying Kathleen "Dixie" Dixon in Casualty. She has also appeared as Rosie in Making Out, Rosemary Mason in Silent Witness, Yvonne Bradley in London's Burning, and as well as roles in Jonathan Creek, The Bill, Doctors, Families, Lovejoy, Coronation Street, and Holby City.
